{{Quote|Widow's blood forces a man's bowels and bladder to fail. He drowns in his own poisons; a slow and painful death. It has earned its name many times, I am sure.|[[Oberyn Martell]]|Poisons (Histories &amp; Lore)}}
'''Widow's blood''' is a [[poison]]. It causes the victim's bowels and bladder to fail and they die a slow and painful death, drowning in their own poisons.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Poisons (Histories &amp; Lore)]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
